f1e40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡欺骗美国 现在拜登需要就如何结束加沙战争做出艰难决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-conned-the-u-s-now-biden-must-make-tough-decisions-on-how-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-11e7-df06-adb8-71e717240000</link><description>经过八个月的推行最终失败的政策后，美国总统乔·拜登可以采取哪些现实且可执行的政策选择来解决冲突？本质上，有两种非常困难的选择——另一种同样令人不安但可行</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-conned-the-u-s-now-biden-must-make-tough-decisions-on-how-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-11e7-df06-adb8-71e717240000</guid></item><item><title>40 枚火箭、5 架无人机、十几起火灾：真主党连续第二天袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/40-rockets-5-drones-a-dozen-fires-hezbollah-pounds-israels-north-for-second-day/00000190-11d1-d529-adb2-37d59cbf0000</link><description>真主党周四向以色列戈兰高地和加利利发射火箭弹、导弹和攻击无人机后，该组织内部消息人士称，这是自加沙战争爆发以来最大规模的袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 15:38:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/40-rockets-5-drones-a-dozen-fires-hezbollah-pounds-israels-north-for-second-day/00000190-11d1-d529-adb2-37d59cbf0000</guid></item><item><title>来自黎巴嫩南部的声音：“我们不支持以色列，但反对真主党的运作方式”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/voices-from-southern-lebanon-we-dont-support-israel-but-oppose-how-hezbollah-operates/00000190-1171-d667-abf0-75fbe3e60000</link><description>黎巴嫩南部居民议论：拉米的生活在真主党向以色列开战的那一天就停止了，纳贾特在生下双胞胎后立即逃离，尼扎尔的村庄正在巡逻以将真主党拒之门外。在南方，悲观情绪盛行</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 14:55:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/voices-from-southern-lebanon-we-dont-support-israel-but-oppose-how-hezbollah-operates/00000190-1171-d667-abf0-75fbe3e60000</guid></item><item><title>受热浪影响，东耶路撒冷巴勒斯坦社区供水减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/water-supply-reduced-in-palestinian-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-amid-heat-wave/00000190-1170-d667-abf0-75fbf3850000</link><description>尽管位于市政线内，卡法阿卡布社区还是从一家巴勒斯坦公司获得水，该公司表示，以色列向其输送的水量减少了。据当地人称，该社区本周只停了两天水。以色列自来水公司：这是巴勒斯坦权力机构的责任</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:31:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/water-supply-reduced-in-palestinian-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-amid-heat-wave/00000190-1170-d667-abf0-75fbf3850000</guid></item></channel></rss>